    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Category: General </p><p>Prerequisite: Proficiency with Light Armor, Level 4+ </p><p>You have trained to master the use of light armor, gaining the following benefits: </p><p>• Increase your Dexterity score by 1, to a maximum of 20.</p><p>• Select one Armor Property from the following; High Quality, Fortified, Reinforced (3).</p><p> Light armor you wear gains the chosen property, if you were not already benefiting from it.</p><p></p>",
